last_episode_to_air.name: Threads of Fate
last_episode_to_air.overview: Jun-woong seeks out the one person who might be able to prevent Ryeon from being dragged to hell. The team still has a job to finish.

name: Tomorrow
overview: Made half-human and half-spirit by accident, a young man is employed by a company of grim reapers in the underworld to carry out special missions.
tagline: Finding a reason to live tomorrow, that's what we do.

episodes.name: Fallen Flower 1
episodes.overview: A dizzying world of hard-at-work grim reapers and an extraordinary offer await Choi Jun-woong after a freak accident lands his body in a coma.

episodes.name: Fallen Flower 2
episodes.overview: While trying to help a TV writer tormented by the return of her high school bully, Jun-woong fails to follow Koo Ryeon's orders to rein in his emotions.

episodes.name: Forest of Time 1
episodes.overview: Jun-woong officially joins Ryeon's team. When his best friend needs saving, he travels back in time and gets a glimpse into a tough childhood.

episodes.name: Forest of Time 2 & Tree 1
episodes.overview: The team sets out to convince both father and son, in the past and present, to rethink their decisions. A runaway soul tells Jun-woong her story.

episodes.name: Tree 2
episodes.overview: The runaway soul refuses to move on until her husband stops blaming himself for her death. As other reapers come after her, Ryeon's team holds them off.

episodes.name: A Soul Becomes a Star
episodes.overview: One day before his death, a war veteran rediscovers the meaning of life as he recounts his journey to Ryeon, Jun-woong and Lim Ryung-gu.

episodes.name: A Prison Without Bars
episodes.overview: The next case surfaces at a cosmetics company. When their tech breaks down, the team uses their observation skills to narrow down the at-risk human.

episodes.name: Broker
episodes.overview: Unable to ignore the discovery of an online scammer who is enabling people to end their lives, Jun-woong takes matters into his own hands.

episodes.name: Someday, Because of You
episodes.overview: An urgent alert leads the grim reapers to an atypical case involving a dog that's been separated from his longtime owner.

episodes.name: Breath
episodes.overview: A woman who was sexually assaulted grapples with trauma, while her twin brother seeks justice. The case proves personal for Ryung-gu.

episodes.name: West Sky 1
episodes.overview: After hearing an awful rumor about Ryung-gu, Jun-woong learns the tragic truth behind his colleague's past, and how he came to be a grim reaper.

episodes.name: West Sky 2
episodes.overview: A familiar face comes up on the team's radar, but her negative energy levels seem to fluctuate irregularly. When Ryung-gu finds out, he steps in.

episodes.name: Spring
episodes.overview: Mutual grief over the pain suffered by a long-lost friend brings two women together. The story of the comfort women and the horrors they endured is told.

episodes.name: Wind Flower
episodes.overview: The sorrows of Ryeon's past come to light. Centuries ago, she was a highborn lady who was left with deep scars after surviving a harrowing event.

episodes.name: Circus
episodes.overview: Helping a tormented top star is an especially important case for Ryeon. Meanwhile, Park Jung-gil demands answers about the secrets being kept from him.
